# 🪢 Hangman Game (Python)

A simple command-line Hangman game built using Python. The player has to guess the hidden word one letter at a time before all lives are lost.

---

## 📌 Features

- Random word selection
- ASCII Hangman graphics
- 7 Lives
- Win/Lose detection
- Large word database
- Beginner-friendly code

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Random Module

---


## 🚀 Future Improvements

- Prevent repeated guesses
- Play Again option
- Difficulty levels
- Hint system
- Scoreboard
- Categories (Animals, Fruits, Countries, etc.)
- GUI using Tkinter
- Sound effects

---

## 📚 Concepts Used

- Variables
- Lists
- Loops
- Conditional Statements
- String Manipulation
- Functions
- Random Module
- While Loop
- User Input
